    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped aubergine</strong>,<strong> courgette</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a very generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and<strong> </strong>a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>dried oregano</strong>, give everything a good mix up and put the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> in the oven for an initial 20 min</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
