    {
      "instruction": "<p>While your veg is cooking, peel and finely chop the<strong> brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
