      "instruction": "<p>While the onion is cooking, peel and finely chop (or grate) the<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve the<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> in 700ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.4L]</span><strong> boiled water</strong></p>",
